# ── ROMs & copyrighted material — NEVER commit these ──────────────────────────
# You must supply your own legally-owned US Super Mario 64 ROM. We never
# redistribute Nintendo ROMs or assets extracted from them.
*.z64
*.n64
*.v64
*.bps
baserom*.z64
baserom*
roms/
# extracted-asset folders (Nintendo-owned media pulled from your ROM at build time)
**/assets/**/*.png
**/assets/**/*.aiff
**/sound/samples/
build/

# ── Rust ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# ── N64Recomp / CMake build output ────────────────────────────────────────────
cmake-build*/
RecompiledFuncs/
recomp/RecompiledFuncs/
*.elf
*.o
*.a

# ── Local runtime / save state (generated locally — never source) ─────────────
*.img
app/saves/*.bin
app/saves/*.sav
app/shadercache/*
!app/shadercache/.gitkeep

# ── macOS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.dSYM/

# ── editors / misc ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log
